data.description: Move in ready! Walking through the front door you'll love the huge living room area and all the brand new laminate flooring throughout the house. The updated kitchen is open to the dining area, has a recent paint job, and a surprise cozy little breakfast nook off to the side. As you make your way upstairs, you'll appreciate the size and closet space of the master bedroom. The second floor also boasts two additional bedrooms and a full bath. Before checking out the rest of the property, don't forget to look at the basement area with another full bathroom, storage space galore, and a sizeable laundry area with access to the carport on the side of the house. Below the house is an additional two story outbuilding with a two car garage with high ceilings and a second floor that needs some finishing touches to become a separate apartment for additional income, a home office space, or the most awesome getaway space of your own! The possibilities are endless!
